            "question": "What are CBD gummies good for?",
            "answer": "<p>CBD gummies are perfect for those moments when you just need to chill, reset, or catch some extra Zzz’s. They’re easy, pre-dosed, and tasty, making them a go-to for stress relief, better sleep, and all-around wellness. Plus, they’re discreet enough to toss in your bag and take anywhere—like a little secret to keep you feeling good on the go.</p>"
