          "type": "faq_block",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are there any side effects from taking CBD gummies?",
            "answer": "<p>Most people vibe well with CBD, but hey, everyone’s body is different! Some folks experience mild effects like drowsiness, dry mouth, or a slight shift in appetite. We recommend starting with a lower dose to see how you feel, and if you have any concerns, reach out to a healthcare provider.</p>"
          }
