          "type": "faq_block",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Will CBD gummies make me high?",
            "answer": "<p>Nope, not a chance. Our CBD gummies are made with hemp-derived CBD, meaning they contain less than 0.3% THC—way too little to make you feel high. So you can enjoy all the wellness benefits of CBD without any of the “heady” vibes. Just pure relaxation, naturally.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_block_jBtPRG": {
          "type": "faq_block",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What’s the difference between CBD gummies and CBD oil tinctures?",
            "answer": "<p>Think of CBD gummies as your low-key, tasty treat that’s ready to go whenever you are. Gummies take a little longer to kick in (usually 30-90 minutes) but offer longer-lasting effects. CBD tinctures, on the other hand, are faster-acting because you drop them under your tongue for quick absorption. So, if you want a quicker boost, tinctures are where it’s at. Want something that feels more like a treat? Gummies are your BFF.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_block_gMVPhf": {
          "type": "faq_block",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How long do CBD gummies last?",
            "answer": "<p>Think of CBD gummies as your low-key, tasty treat that’s ready to go whenever you are. Gummies take a little longer to kick in (usually 30-90 minutes) but offer longer-lasting effects. <a href=\"https://kushqueen.shop/products/bare-cbd-tincture\" title=\"https://kushqueen.shop/products/bare-cbd-tincture\">CBD tinctures</a>, on the other hand, are faster-acting because you drop them under your tongue for quick absorption. So, if you want a quicker boost, tinctures are where it’s at. Want something that feels more like a treat? Gummies are your BFF. Answer</p>"
