          "type": "faq_block",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How long does it take for CBD gummies to work?",
            "answer": "<p>Expect your gummies to start working in about 30 to 90 minutes. Since they’re digested like regular food, they take a bit longer than other forms of CBD, but the effects tend to last longer, too. Perfect for sustained chill!</p>"
